        explain: "The HIR→MIR lowering pass dispatches on HExpr.kind; unknown kinds previously fell through to a children-recurse-then-return-no-value path that silently produced empty MIR. Stage1 punch list C16 — mirror the Gap 14 lower-diag sink convention: emit HX1103 with the unhandled kind so missing constructs (e.g. growable-array method calls, future for/yield desugarings) surface as a precise S2 diagnostic instead of generating a zero-shaped output.",
        fix_it_kind: FixItKind::None
    },
    DiagSpec {
        code: "HX1104",
        title: "closure codegen not yet implemented",
        severity: Severity::Error,
