        explain: "The cited L node was retroactively retired (RFC-017 §5e tombstone + retroactive sweep). The original record stays in atlas history for provenance, but new code may not cite it. See atlas.tombstones.n6 for the full record (replacement, prev_proof_hash, prev_verifier_version). SPEC.yaml atlas_self_discovery.invalidation pins HX1099 as the compile-fail signal.",
