        explain: "The call-site expression's callee resolved to a value whose static type is not a function. Common causes: shadowing a function name with a local let binding, calling a struct field, or accessing a value of a non-fn type as if it were a function. Stage1 punch list C20 surfaces this as HX2003 instead of silently returning unit, so the cascade after Gap 1 multi-file imports stays readable.",
        fix_it_kind: FixItKind::None
